issue.title: UPDATE: Added orange color, Listview UI updated
issue.body:
Updated list layout with cardviews
Adjusted padding, text, alignment and margin for recyclerview, cards, and textfields

Plan to include images and any other info in the rest of white card space. Please let me know if you like the layout or would like some minor changes. 

Next steps:
Images for each animal would have to referenced from the adapter to set for each animal. 

onClick listener interface will need to be included in the adapter and all animal details passed through the adapter via intent to display in the detail page.

Create trivial questions activity


![Screenshot_20190601-015216](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16665280/58745076-5d87c480-8411-11e9-8018-e89a7f1fabef.png)
